com.foreach.across.core.installers

Class InstallerReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.core.installers.InstallerReference

  • public abstract class InstallerReference
extends Object
    Represents the reference to a single installer instance. An installer can be represented either as the actual bean, the class of the installer or the class name of the installer.
    Since:
    5.0.0
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
